title: 8/29/2019 ジコケンTV浴衣配信！ Jikoken TV Ladies' Kimono Fight Night!
description:
ジコケン浴衣配信ご視聴ありがとうございました！沢山の参加者がいてありがたかったです。季節ものは今後もやっていきたいと思います！  

Thanks for watching our yukata (summer kimono) stream! Glad to have so many people come to this event. We'll definitely do more seasonal activities on Jikoken TV in the future!
